node.text:
Next week, I’m going to start periodically publishing my perspectives on current events — uncensored, memorialized to the Blockchain and made available to own, collect, tout and trade as NFTs by freedom lovers like you. Link in bio.

I’m calling it The Non-Fungible Freedom Column.

You can think of this as my version of a New Yorker magazine cover — just with a bit more sarcasm, truth & freedom. ;)

I’m incredibly grateful for this man’s work in the world serving we the people. Biden named him in his list of biggest spreaders of misinformation about the🦠 on the internet. If a tyrant feels threatened by you, you’re doing something magnificent for the people. I’m just jealous I didn’t make his list. I need to work harder.

And thank you @childrenshealthdefense for never backing down from the fight with Goliath. We have so much momentum right now!
#WeThePeople #IWillNotComply

Next week, I’m going to start periodically publishing my perspectives on current events — uncensored, memorialized to the Blockchain and made available to own, collect, tout and trade as NFTs by freedom lovers like you. Link in bio.

You can think of this as my version of a New Yorker magazine cover — just with a bit more sarcasm, truth & freedom. ;)
